title: Muslim Hard-Liners Test Strength in Indonesia Governor’s Race - WSJ
text:
JAKARTA, Indonesia—The most prominent Christian politician in this overwhelmingly Muslim country was fighting for reelection amid his continuing blasphemy trial, as voting got under way Wednesday.
